00:05:56.676 --> 00:05:59.109
ETHAN HEARD: Theater, I was saying 
to the cast, is this miracle.

00:05:59.331 --> 00:06:03.526
Someone's always bound to be sick,
or hurt, or on a late train.

00:06:04.036 --> 00:06:08.020
When everyone is healthy and in the room
and doing the show

00:06:08.292 --> 00:06:09.860
I think that is a miracle.

00:06:10.116 --> 00:06:14.436
to have, you know, 30 collaborators
making a big musical like this happen.

00:06:17.124 --> 00:06:20.325
I think the beautiful thing about 
making theater and sharing theater

00:06:20.582 --> 00:06:23.109
is coming together in a room

00:06:23.365 --> 00:06:26.341
and breathing the same air
and listening to stories

00:06:26.838 --> 00:06:31.972
and reconnecting with 
our shared humanity.

